ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with Mamma Grazzi's Kitchen Ltd** NCC **
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant two options of five years each, commencing on April 1, 2019 and 2024, respectively to extend an existing lease with Mamma Grazzi's Kitchen Ltd., to occupy a property located at 25 George Street, in Ottawa.
